職位，對社會冇咩供獻</blockquote><br />\n死熱狗唔單只對社會冇貢獻，直頭對社會有害，荼毒細蚊仔呃課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩個都係垃圾"},{"pid":"2a93928b697410664f4577d2d2c9b890fc6d6f00","tid":202012,"uid":88120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c545b39537a25f300f6edb372a500f8b0602fd6","tid":202012,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768209c6231083a880548c169d8cdea5c1b29b37","tid":202012,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人做汽水機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d352204fb4d5e1ba0d7b51d920bcb5ee625f5e0","tid":202012,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"咁好心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c203dbc79ddd7bff15dce331b216707d388f26b4","tid":202012,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"慢聯明叔 = 醫生"},{"pid":"b8c307495b7c1ae7f08861a56383c7b496d739db","tid":202012,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>祖赫特: 室內設計公司做admin <br />\n祖赫特: 記者(南極圈)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收到風你依家做緊街邊籌款狗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奇雲道理男友</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女友</blockquote><br />\n大學生lecture hall.wmv</blockquote><br />\n奇雲道爾 ：其實咁樣打燈有CCTV 佢就睇到哂 驚唔驚嫁？<br />\n（含緊）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：影到你個樣<br />\n（含）<br />\n祖赫特：唔好流出去喎。你會呀？<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：梗係想啦。<br />\n祖赫特：唔好啦。流出去就拍咁短，唔想見樣呀。<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：好啦好啦。陣間拍多段。<br />\n（奶粒的+含）<br />\n（用手chok緊，背景有呻吟聲）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：但你幫我含點可以唔見樣？<br />\n祖赫特：咩呀？（手chok緊j)你想影埋我含咩？<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：梗係啦（奇雲道爾fing左兩下j, 祖赫特又含）實見到樣個喎<br />\n祖赫特：我落去啦/唔錄落去啦（呢到聽唔清楚）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：做咩呀？好似巴士咁呀？<br />\n祖赫特：哈<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：好似搭巴士咁呀？（祖赫特隻手chok緊）做咩呀？（隔左陣）<br />\n奇雲道爾 /祖赫特（？）： 都影唔到呢度環境<br />\n奇雲道爾 /祖赫特（？）：真係。影左好似無影到，都唔覺得呢度係課室。哈哈哈<br />\n（鏡頭影住個祖赫特打飛機，之後含返奇雲道爾）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：（呻吟聲）吮死我<br />\n（個鏡頭完全影到祖赫特個樣）<br />\n（之後祖赫特用手捽緊）<br />\n祖赫特：爽死你啦（好細聲）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：係<br />\n（又含）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：（呻吟）<br />\n之後鏡頭轉就無套<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：你個窿呢？<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：你再lam(?)實d<br />\n（鏡頭又轉，入左）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：入左未呀？<br />\n祖赫特：入左（好細聲）<br />\n奇雲道爾 開始搖<br />\n祖赫特：唔好啊x2<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：痛呀？<br />\n（鏡頭再轉，祖赫特狂un）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：（呻吟聲）<br />\n（un左一輪）<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：好近（勁）呀！你夾我呀？我feel到你夾我<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：（呻吟）<br />\n（鏡頭見到祖赫特前後咁毓，之後上下un）<br />\n鏡頭再轉，插到啪啪聲，估計兩個人已全裸<br />\n奇雲道爾 ：嗌啦（啪啪啪x n）<br />\n祖赫特：Hi啦（呻吟）<br />\n鏡頭影到兩人狗仔式，奇雲道爾 應該全裸，祖赫特個件衫去掀到胸上面，下身赤裸<br />\n奇雲道爾 啪緊祖赫特，背景有呻吟聲<br />\n鏡頭又影返祖赫特個pat pat<br />\n全片完<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/05/10/024142_530007ef515b0654398ce645d138ffd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F05%2F10%2F024142_530007ef515b0654398ce645d138ffd9.jpg&h=92ebc01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左=奇雲道爾<br />\n右=祖赫特</blockquote><br />\n好耐冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8928a95ef3ccbf743e5dc0df3e246d400e457fa6","tid":202012,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}